  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the adorable and exciting world of Poly Up! 🐾<br><br>○ Discover the 6 environments currently available!<br>○ Beat your own record and that of others to be the first in the ranking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461280/extras/44cb0645bfcb322d0e138ca9f7405e32.avif?t=1739548298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461280/extras_big/44cb0645bfcb322d0e138ca9f7405e32.avif?t=1739548298 width=800 height=245 /></span><br>🟠 How to play?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >○ Colorful shapes fall from the sky and stack up to create a unique terrain each time you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >○ Jump skillfully on the shapes to climb higher and higher!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >○ But be careful: if a shape lands on your head, the game is over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461280/extras/efab242fb84e0f4eaf137d5a52c8998f.avif?t=1739548298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461280/extras_big/efab242fb84e0f4eaf137d5a52c8998f.avif?t=1739548298 width=800 height=245 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💡 Main features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >○ Simple and addictive gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >○ Animations fluid and delicious visuals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >○ Compete with your friends to dominate the leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to test your reflexes and push your limits in this one-of-a-kind game! How far can you go in Poly Up? 🌟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your climb to the stars now! 🚀</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the adorable and exciting world of Poly Up! 🐾<br><br>○ Discover the 6 environments currently available!<br>○ Beat your own record and that of others to be the first in the ranking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461280/extras/44cb0645bfcb322d0e138ca9f7405e32.avif?t=1739548298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461280/extras_big/44cb0645bfcb322d0e138ca9f7405e32.avif?t=1739548298 width=800 height=245 /></span><br>🟠 How to play?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >○ Colorful shapes fall from the sky and stack up to create a unique terrain each time you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >○ Jump skillfully on the shapes to climb higher and higher!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >○ But be careful: if a shape lands on your head, the game is over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461280/extras/efab242fb84e0f4eaf137d5a52c8998f.avif?t=1739548298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461280/extras_big/efab242fb84e0f4eaf137d5a52c8998f.avif?t=1739548298 width=800 height=245 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💡 Main features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >○ Simple and addictive gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >○ Animations fluid and delicious visuals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >○ Compete with your friends to dominate the leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to test your reflexes and push your limits in this one-of-a-kind game! How far can you go in Poly Up? 🌟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your climb to the stars now! 🚀</p>",
